description.en: Bribe is a cross-chain protocol aiming at bringing liquidity, utility, and aggregate governance rights to algo-stablecoin holders. Bribe introduces liquidity farms, cross-chain bridges, and DAO governance to help the community super-charge their algo-stablecoin holdings and participate in on-chain governance. Governed by $BRIBE token, community and DAO members will earn a share of protocol fees and take an active role in the future of Bribe Protocol.
